TurboMind AI App Icon
======================

This file should be replaced with an actual icon.png file.

Requirements:
- Size: 512x512 pixels
- Format: PNG
- Transparent background recommended
- Name: icon.png

To add your icon:
1. Create icon.png (512x512)
2. Replace this file with your icon.png
3. Update buildozer.spec: icon.filename = assets/icon.png

For now, this is a placeholder.
